"make it SEO friendly."
msgstr ""

#: free/admin/tab-pages/useful_plugins.php:21
msgid "Top Header Section"
msgstr ""

#: free/admin/tab-pages/useful_plugins.php:22
msgid ""
"In the premium version you will get a top header sidebar area where you can "
"use any widget - all the widgets are styled. We have created a number of "
"widgets in the theme which you can use here. Specifically, use the "
"Appointment Info Widget for showing your email ID, contact number or any "
"other info of your choice."
msgstr ""

#: free/admin/tab-pages/useful_plugins.php:29
msgid "Multi Level Navigation"
msgstr ""

#: free/admin/tab-pages/useful_plugins.php:30
msgid ""
"There are beautifully styled navigation/menus in the Appointment theme. You "
"can make multi level menus, which means you can create sub menus."
msgstr ""

